        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "JWT access token from /api/v1/auth/login endpoint. Include in Authorization header as: Bearer <token>. Token expires in 1 hour. Use refresh token to get new access token. Per RFC 7519 (JSON Web Token)."
